      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔称“政策调整时机已到”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/fed-s-powell-says-time-has-come-for-policy-to-adjust</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在怀俄明州杰克逊霍尔举行的美联储年度经济研讨会上表示：“行动的方向很明确，降息的时间和步伐将取决于后续数据、不断变化的前景和风险平衡。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/fed-s-powell-says-time-has-come-for-policy-to-adjust</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:45:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鸽派鲍威尔助长美元 16 个月来最长跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/dovish-powell-adds-fuel-to-dollar-s-longest-plunge-in-16-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席鲍威尔确认央行下个月将降息的预期后，美元暴跌，引发主要全球货币上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/dovish-powell-adds-fuel-to-dollar-s-longest-plunge-in-16-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:44:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英镑兑美元升至两年多以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/pound-hits-strongest-level-in-over-two-years-against-us-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英镑攀升至两年多来的最高水平，进一步推动了英镑在全球范围的上涨，而上涨动力源于市场押注英国央行将比美联储更放松货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/pound-hits-strongest-level-in-over-two-years-against-us-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:09:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔暗示即将降息，黄金价格维持在 2,500 美元以上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/gold-extends-gains-as-powell-signals-rate-cuts-are-coming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔暗示降息时机已到后，金价维持在每盎司 2,500 美元以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/gold-extends-gains-as-powell-signals-rate-cuts-are-coming</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:06:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈萨克斯坦铀矿产量预期“未达标” 铀矿公司股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/investors-rush-into-uranium-miners-on-kazakh-production-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在全球最大的铀生产商哈萨克斯坦国家原子能公司 (Kazatomprom) 发布的业绩指引不及市场预期后，北美专注于铀资源的投资者纷纷大举购买核反应堆燃料矿业公司的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/investors-rush-into-uranium-miners-on-kazakh-production-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 13:24:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国信托银行提出收购要约，台湾银行收购战升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/taiwan-s-bank-takeover-race-heats-up-with-new-bid-for-shin-kong</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾中信金融控股股份有限公司在争夺新光金控股份有限公司的争夺战中加大了赌注，出价近 40 亿美元收购竞争对手的控股权，以打造台湾最大的金融集团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/taiwan-s-bank-takeover-race-heats-up-with-new-bid-for-shin-kong</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 12:48:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博柏利连续 15 年入选富时 100 指数，股价暴跌，近乎终结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/burberry-s-15-year-stay-in-ftse-100-nears-end-after-share-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴宝莉集团 (Burberry Group Plc) 即将退出富时 100 指数，从而结束这家奢侈品制造商在英国蓝筹股指数中长达 15 年的排名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/burberry-s-15-year-stay-in-ftse-100-nears-end-after-share-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 10:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔暗示降息，墨西哥比索引领新兴市场上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/emerging-markets-set-to-cap-weekly-gains-as-traders-await-powell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席鲍威尔表示调整货币政策的时机已经到来，新兴市场股市和货币随之上涨，带动风险资产上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/emerging-markets-set-to-cap-weekly-gains-as-traders-await-powell</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 10:36:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称是时候降息，风险偏好情绪推动油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示现在是降息的时候了，随后油价与风险资产一起上涨，但由于主要经济体的经济前景疲软，油价仍呈周线下跌趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 23:28:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：‘鲍威尔转向’导致债券收益率下降，股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔重申了央行将在 9 月份降息的预期——同时为进一步降息留下空间——之后，股市上涨，债券收益率下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 22:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
